TELEPATHY: Psionic thought communication

Syntax: telepathy <target>
        telepathy <target> <message>
        psi telepathy at <target>

DESCRIPTION:
  Read surface thoughts or send a private psionic message to a target.
  Costs ISP and one APM in combat.

  telepathy <target>
      Use the telepathy psionic power on the target (read thoughts).

  telepathy <target> <message>
      Send a private psionic message to the target.

NOTES:
  You must know the telepathy power and have enough ISP.
  Sending a telepathic message to another player requires that you
  recognize them (use introduce when you meet in person).
  This command delegates to the standard psi path for thought reading.

SEE ALSO: psi, psionics, psihelp, introduce, tell
